            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="12475411">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">”女人有两个生命，我想用生命来想你“</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/12475411/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2011-04-21 23:20</span>
                  
